title: CORRECTED-BRIEF-iQIYI Inc prices IPO of 125 mln ADSs at $18/ADS
text:
March 29, 2018 / 11:56 AM / Updated 6 minutes ago CORRECTED-BRIEF-iQIYI Inc prices IPO of 125 mln ADSs at $18/ADS Reuters Staff 
(Corrects headline to show IPO was priced at $18/ADS not $180/ADS) 
March 29 (Reuters) - Beijing iQIYI Technology Co Ltd: * IQIYI INC. ANNOUNCES PRICING OF INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING 
* IQIYI INC - ‍PRICING IPO OF 125 MILLION ADSS, EACH REPRESENTING SEVEN CLASS A ORDINARY SHARES OF CO, AT A PRICE OF US$18.00 PER ADS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
